{"tid":1684014,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"新口號","createTime":"2019-10-31T01:55:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T09:15:03.000Z","uid":126306,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5ef1cd6bbe340f8c20a5d1860d48623c463c7bd4","tid":1684014,"uid":126306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T01:55:03.000Z","msg":"之前都有人講過<br />\n既然班狗咁鍾意叫人曱甴<br />\n我地就叫番佢地做曱甴<br />\n<br />\n等佢地以後講曱甴都好似講緊自己咁<br />\n目的係令佢地唔敢再講呢個詞語<br />\n甚至聽到曱甴呢兩個字都覺得人地係鬧緊佢地<br />\n<br />\n亦都可以令班藍絲唔敢再亂用呢個詞語<br />\n一用就比人以為鬧班狗曱甴<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">曱甴黑警 解散重整！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\nP.s 口號可以改 諗到更好唔怕講 只係提供一個想法"},{"pid":"27a3f2e8dc0b7bae639b9c54672c649d37406eee","tid":1684014,"uid":320293,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T07:14:41.000Z","msg":"就連bot都唔入黎刷<br />\n善心打破零回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c7f2a09da8a72ffe53389034654e8f6544dc4c0","tid":1684014,"uid":126306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27a3f2e8dc0b7bae639b9c54672c649d37406eee","tid":1684014,"uid":320293,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T07:14:41.000Z","msg":"就連bot都唔入黎刷<br />\n善心打破零回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T08:08:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e9164b68b29858616728b328c77a928b40faba5","tid":1684014,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T08:22:30.000Z","msg":"中意你最後一句"},{"pid":"60c2ead49f4a9e14b3eaeddb08761dfc8b3bc76f","tid":1684014,"uid":126306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e9164b68b29858616728b328c77a928b40faba5","tid":1684014,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T08:22:30.000Z","msg":"中意你最後一句"},"citedBy":0,"rep